events.body: @luke-jr Is it necessary for the Author(s) of the bip to ACK a trivial change like this? If @sipa can confirm that his gist is the correct proposal that was referenced (and I argue should be included for informative/historical context), can this simply be merged?
That's a link to my original proposal, yes.
Yes, authors need to ACK any change...
@gavinandresen, @mikehearn Mind giving this a quick look and an `ACK`? Thank you in advance!

This author is retired, I will not be reviewing any proposed changes.

So.... ACK I suppose?
